description: TEHRAN – President Bashar al Assad of Syria visited Tehran on Thursday to offer condolences to Leader of Islamic Revolution Ayatollah Ali Khamenei over the tragic death of President Ebrahim Raisi in a helicopter crash on May 19.
title: Syrian president meets Ayatollah Khamenei to offer condolences over Raisi death

description: TEHRAN – Registration began on Thursday for those who hopefuls who intend to compete in the snap presidential election following the death of President Ebrahim Raisi in a helicopter crash on May 19.
title: Iran begins candidate registration for snap presidential election

description: Leader of the Islamic Revolution Ayatollah Seyyed Ali Khamenei has addressed a letter to pro-Palestinian students across the United States, hailing their struggle and considering them to be part of the global resistance movement.
title: Leader to pro-Palestinian US students: You’re standing on the right side of history
